description:
On episode 55 and the first installment of the ALL THE SMOKE Girdiron series, Matt and Stephen are joined by Super Bowl winning Chiefs tight end Travis Kelce. Kelce talks about having Patrick Mahomes as his QB, winning the Super Bowl, and discusses his new teammate LeVeon Bell.
